  "keyFeatures": [
    "Interactive drag-and-drop timeline",
    "Task dependencies and links",
    "Hierarchical subtasks (summary tasks)",
    "Configurable time scales (hours, days, weeks, months)",
    "Customizable grid columns with inline editors",
    "Toolbar, context menu, and task editor",
    "Tooltips for taskbars",
    "Zoom with scroll and configurable zoom levels",
    "Hotkey support for common actions",
    "Multi-column sorting",
    "Localization support",
    "Full TypeScript support",
    "React 19 compatibility",
    "High performance with large datasets (10k+ tasks)",
    "Light/dark theme support (Material, Willow, WillowDark)",
    "PRO: Auto-scheduling, critical path, baselines, split tasks, undo/redo, export"
